'''流星飛彈'''是一種由英國、法國、德國和義大利合資成立的MBDA公司研製，並於2016年服役的[[主動雷達導引|主動雷達導引]][[超視距作戰|超視距]][[空對空飛彈|空對空飛彈]]。

流星能提供多重射擊能力（針對多個目標進行多次發射），並有能力與高機動的目標交戰，例如噴射機和小型目標，如無人機和射程超過{{convert|100|km|nmi|abbr=}}在高強度{{link-en|電子反制裝置|electronic countermeasures}}環境中的巡航導彈。<ref name="range"/>固體燃料衝壓引擎容許導彈以超過4馬赫的速度巡航，併為導彈提供推力於中途加速去攔截目標。<ref>{{cite web |title=Meteor |url=https://www.mbda-systems.com/product/meteor/ |website=mbda-systems.com |access-date=4 March 2019 |archive-date=2021-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211119032110/https://www.mbda-systems.com/product/meteor/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=The Most Advanced Air-to-Air Missile In The World |url=https://saab.com/gripen/news/blog/gripen-blog/2019/quick-launch-gripen-the-most-advanced-air-to-air-missile-in-the-world/ |website=saab.com |access-date=4 March 2019 |archive-date=2019-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190306111427/https://saab.com/gripen/news/blog/gripen-blog/2019/quick-launch-gripen-the-most-advanced-air-to-air-missile-in-the-world/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 流星的雙向數據鏈使得引擎能夠提供導彈在飛行中途更新目標或在需要時重新定位，資訊包括來自非機載的第三方數據。數據鏈能夠傳輸導彈資訊，如功能和運動狀態、多個目標的資訊以及自動導引彈頭探測到目標的通知。<ref name="SAAB Meteor">{{cite web |title=Meteor - Beyond visual range air-to-air missile |url=https://saab.com/air/weapon-systems/air-to-air-missile-systems/meteor/ |website=saab.com |access-date=4 March 2019 |archive-date=2019-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190306044323/https://saab.com/air/weapon-systems/air-to-air-missile-systems/meteor/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 據MBDA聲稱，流星的動力性能是目前同類空對空導彈的三到六倍。性能的關鍵是由德國{{link-en|拜仁-化工|MBDA Deutschland GmbH}}製造的可節流式{{link-en|導管火箭|Air-augmented rocket}}([[衝壓發動機|衝壓引擎]])。<ref name="Meteor">{{Citation |url=http://www.defense-update.com/newscast/0308/news/news2103_meteor.htm |title=European Meteor BVRaam Missile Test Fired over Sweden |newspaper=Defense update |access-date=2008-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080515160907/http://www.defense-update.com/newscast/0308/news/news2103_meteor.htm |archive-date=2008-05-15 |url-status=dead }}</ref>

流星導彈於2016年4月首度在[[瑞典空軍|瑞典空軍]][[JAS_39獅鷲戰鬥機|JAS 39獅鷲戰鬥機]]上服役，2016年7月正式具備初始作戰能力（IOC）。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.upi.com/Business_News/Security-Industry/2016/07/11/Swedish-AF-Gripens-now-carry-Meteor-missiles/5341468254872/?st_rec=9021468503609|title=Swedish AF Gripens now carry Meteor missiles|access-date=2016-07-18|archive-date=2016-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160808050005/http://www.upi.com/Business_News/Security-Industry/2016/07/11/Swedish-AF-Gripens-now-carry-Meteor-missiles/5341468254872/?st_rec=9021468503609|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Citation |title=Aviation week |date=October 7, 2012 |url=http://www.aviationweek.com/Article.aspx?id=/article-xml/awx_07_10_2012_p0-475096.xml&p=2 |accessdate=2022-01-08 |archive-date=2014-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140118003048/http://www.aviationweek.com/Article.aspx?id=%2Farticle-xml%2Fawx_07_10_2012_p0-475096.xml&p=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/paris-mbda-on-target-for-meteor-introduction-413687/|title=PARIS: MBDA on target for Meteor introduction|work=Flightglobal.com|access-date=30 January 2016|archive-date=2018-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181125204533/https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/paris-mbda-on-target-for-meteor-introduction-413687/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2018年[[英國皇家空軍|英國皇家空軍]]開始裝備流星導彈在[[颱風戰鬥機|颱風戰鬥機]]上，直到2021年為止，裝備流星導彈的空軍包括; [[德國聯邦國防軍空軍|德國聯邦國防軍空軍]]、[[西班牙空軍|西班牙空軍]]和{{link-en|義大利空軍|Italian Air Force}}的[[颱風戰鬥機|颱風戰鬥機]]，[[法國空天軍|法國空天軍]]和[[印度空軍|印度空軍]]的[[飆風戰鬥機|疾風戰鬥機]]。[[英國皇家空軍|英國皇家空軍]]亦計劃於2024年在[[F-35閃電II戰鬥機|F-35閃電II戰鬥機]]配備流星導彈。未來將會裝備的用戶包括;[[希臘空軍|希臘空軍]]、[[沙烏地阿拉伯皇家空軍|沙烏地阿拉伯皇家空軍]]、[[卡達皇家空軍|卡達皇家空軍]]、[[韓國空軍|韓國空軍]]、{{link-en|巴西空軍|Brazilian Air Force}}與[[英國皇家海軍|英國皇家海軍]]等。<ref name="George Allison">{{cite web|url=https://ukdefencejournal.org.uk/saudi-arabia-purchases-meteor-missiles/|title=Saudi Arabia purchases Meteor missiles|author=George Allison|work=UK Defence Journal|date=4 February 2015|access-date=30 January 2016|archive-date=2017-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171122120235/https://ukdefencejournal.org.uk/saudi-arabia-purchases-meteor-missiles/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="auto">{{cite web|url=http://defenceaviationpost.com/iafs-rafale-fighter-jets-france-come-equipped-meteors/|title=IAFs Rafale fighter jets from France to come equipped with Meteors - Defence Aviation Post|date=14 September 2016|work=defenceaviationpost.com |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160916190740/http://defenceaviationpost.com/iafs-rafale-fighter-jets-france-come-equipped-meteors/| archive-date=2016-09-16 |url-status=dead}}</ref>,<ref name="airrecognition.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.airrecognition.com/index.php/focus-analysis-photo-report-aviation-defence-industry/air-force-in-the-world/1745-qatar-emiri-air-force-to-get-the-full-range-of-mbda-missiles-for-its-24-rafale-fighters-0705152.html|title=Qatar Emiri Air Force To Get The Full Range of MBDA Missiles for its 24 Rafale fighters 0705152|work=airrecognition.com|access-date=30 January 2016|archive-date=2017-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170704005658/http://airrecognition.com/index.php/focus-analysis-photo-report-aviation-defence-industry/air-force-in-the-world/1745-qatar-emiri-air-force-to-get-the-full-range-of-mbda-missiles-for-its-24-rafale-fighters-0705152.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref name="La Tribune">{{cite news |title=Le Brésil va acheter une centaine de missiles air-air Meteor à MBDA pour ses Gripen NG |url=https://www.latribune.fr/entreprises-finance/industrie/aeronautique-defense/le-bresil-va-acheter-une-centaine-de-missiles-air-air-meteor-a-mbda-pour-ses-gripen-ng-819389.html |publisher=La Tribune |language=fr |date=5 May 2019 |accessdate=2021-09-20 |archive-date=2021-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211115192452/https://www.latribune.fr/entreprises-finance/industrie/aeronautique-defense/le-bresil-va-acheter-une-centaine-de-missiles-air-air-meteor-a-mbda-pour-ses-gr